19	"Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari" mavzusida ma`naviy-ma`rifiy tadbir bo`lib o`tdi!	"Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari" mavzusida ma`naviy-ma`rifiy tadbir bo`lib o`tdi!	An event on the topic "Alisher Navoi and Mirzo Bobur - Great Figures of the Timurid Renaissance" took place!	Мероприятие на тему "Алишер Навои и Мирзо Бобур - великие представители Тимуридского Возрождения" состоялось!	"Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari" mavzusida ma‘naviy-ma‘rifiy tadbir bo‘lib o‘tdi!	<p>Perfect Universiteti, O`zbekiston Respublikasi Mudofaa Vazirligi, O`zbekiston Yozuvchilar uyushmasi va Temuriylar Tarixi Davlat Muzeyi, Milliy Tiklanish Demokratik Partiyasi, O&#39;zbekiston Davlat akademik drama teatri bilan hamkorlikda &quot;Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari&quot; mavzusida ma`naviy-ma`rifiy tadbir bo`lib o`tdi! Tadbir O`zbekiston Respublikasi Qurolli Kuchlar Bosh Harbiy Klinik Gospitalining katta konferensiya zalida tashkil etilib ushbu ikki alloma haqida va ularning merosi haqida fikr almashilindi. Qiziqarli savollar bilan yakunlangan tadbir to`g`ri javob egalariga va tashkilotchilarga estalik sovg`alari topshirildi! &quot;Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari&quot; mavzusida bo`lib o`tgan ma`naviy-ma`rifiy tadbir talabalarimiz va boshqa ishtirokchilar ko`nglida ilmga bo`lgan hurmat va shijoat hislatlarini jo`shqinlantirib ertangi kun uchun yana bir muvaffaqiyat omili bo`lib xizmat qiladi albatta! Chunki mukammal kelajak sifatli ta`lim bilan amalga oshajak, allomalarimiz kabi!</p>	<p>Perfect Universiteti, O`zbekiston Respublikasi Mudofaa Vazirligi, O`zbekiston Yozuvchilar uyushmasi va Temuriylar Tarixi Davlat Muzeyi, Milliy Tiklanish Demokratik Partiyasi, O&#39;zbekiston Davlat akademik drama teatri bilan hamkorlikda &quot;Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari&quot; mavzusida ma`naviy-ma`rifiy tadbir bo`lib o`tdi! Tadbir O`zbekiston Respublikasi Qurolli Kuchlar Bosh Harbiy Klinik Gospitalining katta konferensiya zalida tashkil etilib ushbu ikki alloma haqida va ularning merosi haqida fikr almashilindi. Qiziqarli savollar bilan yakunlangan tadbir to`g`ri javob egalariga va tashkilotchilarga estalik sovg`alari topshirildi! &quot;Alisher Navoiy va Mirzo Bobur - Temuriylar Renessansining yirik namoyondalari&quot; mavzusida bo`lib o`tgan ma`naviy-ma`rifiy tadbir talabalarimiz va boshqa ishtirokchilar ko`nglida ilmga bo`lgan hurmat va shijoat hislatlarini jo`shqinlantirib ertangi kun uchun yana bir muvaffaqiyat omili bo`lib xizmat qiladi albatta! Chunki mukammal kelajak sifatli ta`lim bilan amalga oshajak, allomalarimiz kabi!</p>	<p>At &quot;Perfect University&quot;, under the Ministry of Defense of the Republic of Uzbekistan, in collaboration with the Writers&#39; Association of Uzbekistan, the State Museum of Timurid History, the National Democratic Party, and in partnership with the Uzbek State Academic Drama Theater, a spiritual and educational event on the theme &quot;Alisher Navoi and Mirzo Bobur - Great Representatives of the Timurid Renaissance&quot; took place! The event was held in the large conference hall of the Central Clinical Hospital of the Armed Forces of the Republic of Uzbekistan, where their lives and achievements were discussed. Concluding with interesting questions and answers, the event ended with the presentation of appreciation gifts to those who answered correctly and to the organizers! This spiritual and educational event on the theme &quot;Alisher Navoi and Mirzo Bobur - Great Representatives of the Timurid Renaissance&quot; will undoubtedly be another successful contribution to enriching the knowledge and respect for our students and other participants! Because the future of enlightenment in our education will surely continue, just like our achievements!</p>	<p>